name: unholy birth
description:
"Such a rainy day with such beautiful friends. Lots of sweet land creatures we experienced that day. I can not forget how beautiful when the screams and thunder getting together like a great recital, giving by suffering and pain. The pain which we cause, by the way... I can proudly say, this was my first and also my best day in life. First blood is always the best... Love ya, my sweet family, mom, dad and lovely friends... I wish you all wonderful times like this soon.

Kisses from your lovely son and pal...

Octopus head..."

Tried to write and perform the voice of an imaginary creature I named Octopus Head(of course highly inspired by Lovecraft`s Cthulhu :) ) with a music I made with an old broken guitar in my hometown :) I really enjoyed making this story and illustration, hope you enjoy it too :)
